Package: SITH
Type: Package
Title: A Spatial Model of Intra-Tumor Heterogeneity
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Date: 2020-05-26
Author: Phillip B. Nicol
Maintainer: Phillip B. Nicol <philnicol740@gmail.com>
Description: Implements a three-dimensional stochastic model of cancer growth and mutation. Allows for interactive 3D visualizations of the simulated tumor. Provides a comprehensive summary on the spatial distribution of mutants within the tumor. Contains functions which create simulated sequencing datasets from the generated tumor. 
License: GPL (>= 2)
Depends: R (>= 4.0.0)
Imports: 
    Rcpp (>= 1.0.4),
    scatterplot3d,
    stats,
    graphics,
    grDevices      
Suggests: 
    rgl,
    knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    testthat
LinkingTo: Rcpp
RoxygenNote: 7.1.0
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Encoding: UTF-8
URL: https://github.com/phillipnicol/3dITH
BugReports: https://github.com/phillipnicol/3dITH/issues
